cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM

The paper deals with 3D shape matching and deformation using deep learning techniques. This falls under the domain of computer vision (cs.CV) and computer graphics (cs.GR). The use of deep learning models for encoding and predicting correspondences suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the use of 3D meshes and surface representations suggests a possible connection to multimedia (cs.MM).
